Restful API for creating Tokens

GET /tokens  - return a list of all tokens known to the server - don't want
*GET /tokens/:id - return just a single token - do want
*POST /tokens - creates a new token - do want
PUT /tokens/:id - updates a single token - don't need just now
DELETE /tokens/:id - deletes a single token - don't need just now


GET /tokens - have the form in this view -> not done
POST /tokens
GET /tokens/:id - human version

GET /api/tokens/:id - just returns JSON for the phone app